                    <p><strong class="text-navy">Week 3:</strong> Increase intensity. Slower negatives (3 sec down). Skin should show results.</p>
                    <p><strong class="text-navy">Week 4:</strong> Max out. Test your new Pushup/Pullup max. "Prime Polish".</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

